docs.lead_paragraph: BUENOS AIRES, April 9--The peronista bloc in the Chamber of Deputies voted in caucus tonight for the expropriation of La Prensa after having heard a report of the joint Congressional committee that has been investigating the paper. The vote was by acclamation. Ninety-eight deputies were present.
